metadata.description: Winning auction team Matthew Liu and Josh Fraser, co-founders of Origin Protocol, outbid Oscar-winning actor Leonardo DiCaprio to win the first-ever CORE NFT Selfie at the CORE Gala in Miami Beach, Soho House during Art Basel 2021. This NFT, which received coverage in the New York Times, was created by artist Reka Nyari and raised $200,000 towards COVID relief efforts. Included in the portrait are Josh Fraser, Matthew Liu, Sean Penn, Marc Anthony, Alicia Machado, Patricia Velasquez, Soleil Moon Fry, Eglantina Zingg, Clinton Lau, and Henry Lau. Created in partnership with Metagood, the NFT platform for Social Good. Edition 1 of 2. Copyright 2021 Reka Nyari
metadata.name: CORE Celebrity Selfie 1/2
